==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ignescent
<hw>Ig*nes"cent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>ignescens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>ignescere</ets> to become inflamed,
fr. <ets>ignis</ets> fire: cf. F. <ets>ignescent</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Emitting sparks of fire when struck with steel; scintillating;
<as>as, <ex>ignescent</ex> stones</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ignicolist</ent>⟦br⟧
